4. As all Buddhas refrained from false speech until the end of their lives, so I too will refrain from false speech until the end of my life.
Simp. Chinese: <ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb>如</rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-family /**/:inherit;">Rú</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> <ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb>诸</rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-family /**/:inherit;">zhū</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> <ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb>佛</rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-family /**/:inherit;">Fó</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> <ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb>尽</rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-family /**/:inherit;">jìn</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> <ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb>寿</rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-family /**/:inherit;">shòu</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> <ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb>不</rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-family /**/:inherit;">bù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> <ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb>妄</rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-family /**/:inherit;">wàng</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> <ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb>语</rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode M